{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852280578,"sessionID":"ses_286f4e666ffednMOyI47LTqQHL","part":{"id":"prt_d790b542a001xG6yjGmtTK3IMa","messageID":"msg_d790b44d3001XurbNOocEBgKTP","sessionID":"ses_286f4e666ffednMOyI47LTqQHL","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-e84726d1440e45e89c133cb248774bff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/router`\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## Overview\n8: 为 Router 模块添加 JWT 认证与签发能力，包括 Token 签发、验证和刷新功能。\n9: \n10: ## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n11: ### Requirement: JWT Token 签发\n12: #### Scenario: 使用 HS256 算法签发 Token\n13: - **GIVEN** 配置了有效的 HS256 密钥\n14: - **WHEN** 调用 Sign 方法签发 Token\n15: - **THEN** 返回有效的 JWT Token\n16: \n17: #### Scenario: 使用 RS256 算法签发 Token\n18: - **GIVEN** 配置了有效的 RSA 密钥对\n19: - **WHEN** 调用 Sign 方法签发 Token\n20: - **THEN** 返回有效的 JWT Token\n21: \n22: ### Requirement: JWT Token 验证\n23: #### Scenario: 验证有效 Token\n24: - **GIVEN** 有效的 JWT Token\n25: - **WHEN** 调用 Verify 方法验证 Token\n26: - **THEN** 返回解析后的 Claims\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: 拒绝过期 Token\n29: - **GIVEN** 已过期的 JWT Token\n30: - **WHEN** 调用 Verify 方法验证 Token\n31: - **THEN** 返回 ErrTokenExpired 错误\n32: \n33: #### Scenario: 拒绝篡改 Token\n34: - **GIVEN** 被篡改的 JWT Token\n35: - **WHEN** 调用 Verify 方法验证 Token\n36: - **THEN** 返回 ErrTokenInvalid 错误\n37: \n38: ### Requirement: Token 刷新\n39: #### Scenario: 刷新有效 Token\n40: - **GIVEN** 有效的 Refresh Token\n41: - **WHEN** 调用 Refresh 方法\n42: - **THEN** 返回新的 TokenPair\n43: \n44: #### Scenario: 拒绝无效刷新\n45: - **GIVEN** 无效或过期的 Refresh Token\n46: - **WHEN** 调用 Refresh 方法\n47: - **THEN** 返回 ErrTokenRefreshFailed 错误\n48: \n49: ### Requirement: 认证中间件\n50: #### Scenario: 通过有效 Token 的请求\n51: - **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含有效 Authorization Header\n52: - **WHEN** 请求经过 AuthMiddleware\n53: - **THEN** 请求被放行，Claims 注入上下文\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: 拒绝无 Token 的请求\n56: - **GIVEN** HTTP 请求不包含 Authorization Header\n57: - **WHEN** 请求经过 AuthMiddleware\n58: - **THEN** 返回 401 Unauthorized 响应\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: 拒绝无效 Token 的请求\n61: - **GIVEN** HTTP 请求包含无效 Token\n62: - **WHEN** 请求经过 AuthMiddleware\n63: - **THEN** 返回 401 Unauthorized 响应\n64: \n65: ## Implementation Files\n66: | File | Purpose |\n67: |------|---------|\n68: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWT 核心功能（Sign/Verify/Refresh） |\n69: | `pkg/router/jwt_test.go` | JWT 单元测试 |\n70: | `pkg/router/middleware/auth.go` | HTTP 认证中间件 |\n71: | `pkg/router/middleware/auth_test.go` | 中间件测试 |\n72: \n73: ## Dependencies\n74: | Package | Purpose |\n75: |---------|---------|\n76: | github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 | JWT 标准库 |\n77: | pkg/config | 配置管理 |\n78: | pkg/logger | 日志记录 |\n79: \n80: ## Validation Checklist\n81: - [ ] JWT Token 签发功能正常\n82: - [ ] Token 验证中间件正确拦截无效请求\n83: - [ ] Token 刷新机制工作正常\n84: - [ ] 支持 HS256 和 RS256 算法\n85: - [ ] 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n86: - [ ] 无安全漏洞（密钥不硬编码）\n\n(End of file - total 86 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n**Module:** `pkg/router`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** M\n\n## Overview\n为 Router 模块添加 JWT 认证与签发能力，包括 Token 签发、验证和刷新功能。\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n### Requirement: JWT Token 签发\n#### Scenario: 使用 HS256 算法签发 Token\n- **GIVEN** 配置了有效的 HS256 密钥\n- **WHEN** 调用 Sign 方法签发 Token\n- **THEN** 返回有效的 JWT Token\n\n#### Scenario: 使用 RS256 算法签发 Token\n- **GIVEN** 配置了有效的 RSA 密钥对\n- **WHEN** 调用 Sign 方法签发 Token\n- **THEN** 返回有效的 JWT Token","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775852280558,"end":1775852280576}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852280581,"sessionID":"ses_286f4e666ffednMOyI47LTqQHL","part":{"id":"prt_d790b574f001Y37CtmmVJndgcX","messageID":"msg_d790b44d3001XurbNOocEBgKTP","sessionID":"ses_286f4e666ffednMOyI47LTqQHL","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-9270448e3ff74a2691d470d407ab19f2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package router\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"context\"\n5: \t\"crypto/rand\"\n6: \t\"crypto/rsa\"\n7: \t\"crypto/x509\"\n8: \t\"encoding/pem\"\n9: \t\"fmt\"\n10: \t\"os\"\n11: \t\"time\"\n12: \n13: \t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n14: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n15: )\n16: \n17: const (\n18: \trsaKeySize         = 2048\n19: \tjwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n20: \tIdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n21: \tPrivateKeyDataKey  = \"private.pem\"\n22: \tPublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n23: )\n24: \n25: var IdentityNamespace = \"default\"\n26: \n27: func init() {\n28: \tif ns := os.Getenv(\"AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\"); ns != \"\" {\n29: \t\tIdentityNamespace = ns\n30: \t}\n31: }\n32: \n33: type JWTManager struct {\n34: \tprivateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n35: \tpublicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n36: }\n37: \n38: func NewJWTManager() (*JWTManager, error) {\n39: \tprivateKey, err := rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)\n40: \tif err != nil {\n41: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to generate RSA key: %w\", err)\n42: \t}\n43: \n44: \treturn &JWTManager{\n45: \t\tprivateKey: privateKey,\n46: \t\tpublicKey:  &privateKey.PublicKey,\n47: \t}, nil\n48: }\n49: \n50: func (j *JWTManager) GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{}) (string, error) {\n51: \tnow := time.Now()\n52: \n53: \ttokenClaims := jwt.MapClaims{\n54: \t\t\"exp\": now.Add(jwtExpiration).Unix(),\n55: \t\t\"iat\": now.Unix(),\n56: \t\t\"iss\": \"agentcube-router\",\n57: \t}\n58: \n59: \tfor k, v := range claims {\n60: \t\ttokenClaims[k] = v\n61: \t}\n62: \n63: \ttoken := jwt.NewWithClaims(jwt.SigningMethodRS256, tokenClaims)\n64: \n65: \ttokenString, err := token.SignedString(j.privateKey)\n66: \tif err != nil {\n67: \t\treturn \"\", &JWTSigningError{Err: err}\n68: \t}\n69: \n70: \treturn tokenString, nil\n71: }\n72: \n73: func (j *JWTManager) TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx context.Context) error {\n74: \tklog.Warningf(\"not in cluster, skipping secret persistence\")\n75: \treturn nil\n76: }\n77: \n78: func encodePrivateKeyPEM(key *rsa.PrivateKey) []byte {\n79: \treturn pem.EncodeToMemory(&pem.Block{\n80: \t\tType:  \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\",\n81: \t\tBytes: x509.MarshalPKCS1PrivateKey(key),\n82: \t})\n83: }\n84: \n85: func encodePublicKeyPEM(key *rsa.PublicKey) []byte {\n86: \tbytes, err := x509.MarshalPKIXPublicKey(key)\n87: \tif err != nil {\n88: \t\treturn nil\n89: \t}\n90: \treturn pem.EncodeToMemory(&pem.Block{\n91: \t\tType:  \"PUBLIC KEY\",\n92: \t\tBytes: bytes,\n93: \t})\n94: }\n95: \n96: func loadPrivateKeyPEM(data []byte) (*rsa.PrivateKey, error) {\n97: \tblock, _ := pem.Decode(data)\n98: \tif block == nil {\n99: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to decode PEM block\")\n100: \t}\n101: \n102: \tkey, err := x509.ParsePKCS1PrivateKey(block.Bytes)\n103: \tif err != nil {\n104: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse private key: %w\", err)\n105: \t}\n106: \n107: \treturn key, nil\n108: }\n109: \n110: func (j *JWTManager) GetPublicKey() *rsa.PublicKey {\n111: \treturn j.publicKey\n112: }\n\n(End of file - total 112 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package router\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"crypto/rand\"\n\t\"crypto/rsa\"\n\t\"crypto/x509\"\n\t\"encoding/pem\"\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n)\n\nconst (\n\trsaKeySize         = 2048\n\tjwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n\tIdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt.go","time":{"start":1775852280561,"end":1775852280579}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852280584,"sessionID":"ses_286f4e666ffednMOyI47LTqQHL","part":{"id":"prt_d790b5ad2001r7jF6kY3YOlNvu","messageID":"msg_d790b44d3001XurbNOocEBgKTP","sessionID":"ses_286f4e666ffednMOyI47LTqQHL","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-574941436d8b457f9b1cdc773765b4db","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt_test.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt_test.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package router\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"testing\"\n5: \t\"time\"\n6: \n7: \t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n8: )\n9: \n10: func TestNewJWTManager(t *testing.T) {\n11: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n12: \tif err != nil {\n13: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n14: \t}\n15: \tif jwtMgr.privateKey == nil {\n16: \t\tt.Error(\"privateKey is nil\")\n17: \t}\n18: \tif jwtMgr.publicKey == nil {\n19: \t\tt.Error(\"publicKey is nil\")\n20: \t}\n21: }\n22: \n23: func TestJWTManagerGenerateToken(t *testing.T) {\n24: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n25: \tif err != nil {\n26: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n27: \t}\n28: \n29: \tclaims := map[string]interface{}{\n30: \t\t\"session_id\": \"test-session\",\n31: \t\t\"sandbox_id\": \"test-sandbox\",\n32: \t}\n33: \n34: \ttokenStr, err := jwtMgr.GenerateToken(claims)\n35: \tif err != nil {\n36: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to generate token: %v\", err)\n37: \t}\n38: \n39: \ttoken, err := jwt.Parse(tokenStr, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n40: \t\tif _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA); !ok {\n41: \t\t\treturn nil, jwt.ErrSignatureInvalid\n42: \t\t}\n43: \t\treturn jwtMgr.publicKey, nil\n44: \t})\n45: \n46: \tif err != nil {\n47: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to parse token: %v\", err)\n48: \t}\n49: \n50: \tif !token.Valid {\n51: \t\tt.Error(\"token is not valid\")\n52: \t}\n53: \n54: \tmapClaims, ok := token.Claims.(jwt.MapClaims)\n55: \tif !ok {\n56: \t\tt.Fatal(\"claims are not MapClaims\")\n57: \t}\n58: \n59: \tif mapClaims[\"iss\"] != \"agentcube-router\" {\n60: \t\tt.Errorf(\"unexpected issuer: %v\", mapClaims[\"iss\"])\n61: \t}\n62: \n63: \tif mapClaims[\"session_id\"] != \"test-session\" {\n64: \t\tt.Errorf(\"unexpected session_id: %v\", mapClaims[\"session_id\"])\n65: \t}\n66: }\n67: \n68: func TestJWTManagerTokenExpiration(t *testing.T) {\n69: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n70: \tif err != nil {\n71: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n72: \t}\n73: \n74: \ttokenStr, err := jwtMgr.GenerateToken(map[string]interface{}{})\n75: \tif err != nil {\n76: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to generate token: %v\", err)\n77: \t}\n78: \n79: \ttoken, err := jwt.Parse(tokenStr, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n80: \t\treturn jwtMgr.publicKey, nil\n81: \t})\n82: \n83: \tif err != nil {\n84: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to parse token: %v\", err)\n85: \t}\n86: \n87: \tmapClaims, ok := token.Claims.(jwt.MapClaims)\n88: \tif !ok {\n89: \t\tt.Fatal(\"claims are not MapClaims\")\n90: \t}\n91: \n92: \texp, ok := mapClaims[\"exp\"].(float64)\n93: \tif !ok {\n94: \t\tt.Fatal(\"exp claim is not float64\")\n95: \t}\n96: \n97: \tnow := time.Now().Unix()\n98: \texpectedExp := now + int64(jwtExpiration.Seconds())\n99: \n100: \tif int64(exp) < now {\n101: \t\tt.Error(\"token is already expired\")\n102: \t}\n103: \n104: \tif int64(exp) > expectedExp+5 || int64(exp) < expectedExp-5 {\n105: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expiration time is not approximately 5 minutes: exp=%d, expected=%d\", int64(exp), expectedExp)\n106: \t}\n107: }\n108: \n109: func TestJWTManagerGetPublicKey(t *testing.T) {\n110: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n111: \tif err != nil {\n112: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n113: \t}\n114: \n115: \tpubKey := jwtMgr.GetPublicKey()\n116: \tif pubKey == nil {\n117: \t\tt.Error(\"GetPublicKey returned nil\")\n118: \t}\n119: \n120: \tif pubKey.Size() != 2048/8 {\n121: \t\tt.Errorf(\"unexpected key size: %d\", pubKey.Size())\n122: \t}\n123: }\n124: \n125: func TestEncodePrivateKeyPEM(t *testing.T) {\n126: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n127: \tif err != nil {\n128: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n129: \t}\n130: \n131: \tpemData := encodePrivateKeyPEM(jwtMgr.privateKey)\n132: \tif pemData == nil {\n133: \t\tt.Fatal(\"encodePrivateKeyPEM returned nil\")\n134: \t}\n135: \n136: \tif !contains(string(pemData), \"RSA PRIVATE KEY\") {\n137: \t\tt.Errorf(\"PEM data does not contain 'RSA PRIVATE KEY'\")\n138: \t}\n139: }\n140: \n141: func TestEncodePublicKeyPEM(t *testing.T) {\n142: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n143: \tif err != nil {\n144: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n145: \t}\n146: \n147: \tpemData := encodePublicKeyPEM(jwtMgr.publicKey)\n148: \tif pemData == nil {\n149: \t\tt.Fatal(\"encodePublicKeyPEM returned nil\")\n150: \t}\n151: \n152: \tif !contains(string(pemData), \"PUBLIC KEY\") {\n153: \t\tt.Errorf(\"PEM data does not contain 'PUBLIC KEY'\")\n154: \t}\n155: }\n156: \n157: func TestLoadPrivateKeyPEM(t *testing.T) {\n158: \tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n159: \tif err != nil {\n160: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n161: \t}\n162: \n163: \tpemData := encodePrivateKeyPEM(jwtMgr.privateKey)\n164: \tloadedKey, err := loadPrivateKeyPEM(pemData)\n165: \tif err != nil {\n166: \t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to load private key: %v\", err)\n167: \t}\n168: \n169: \tif loadedKey.N.Cmp(jwtMgr.privateKey.N) != 0 {\n170: \t\tt.Error(\"loaded key does not match original key\")\n171: \t}\n172: }\n173: \n174: func TestLoadPrivateKeyPEMInvalid(t *testing.T) {\n175: \t_, err := loadPrivateKeyPEM([]byte(\"invalid pem data\"))\n176: \tif err == nil {\n177: \t\tt.Error(\"expected error for invalid PEM data\")\n178: \t}\n179: }\n180: \n181: func contains(s, substr string) bool {\n182: \treturn len(s) > 0 && len(substr) > 0 && len(s) >= len(substr)\n183: }\n\n(End of file - total 183 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package router\n\nimport (\n\t\"testing\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n)\n\nfunc TestNewJWTManager(t *testing.T) {\n\tjwtMgr, err := NewJWTManager()\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\tt.Fatalf(\"failed to create JWTManager: %v\", err)\n\t}\n\tif jwtMgr.privateKey == nil {\n\t\tt.Error(\"privateKey is nil\")\n\t}\n\tif jwtMgr.publicKey == nil {\n\t\tt.Error(\"publicKey is nil\")\n\t}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/router/jwt_test.go","time":{"start":1775852280564,"end":1775852280581}}}}
